Question: Are both the tape and the keyboard made of the same material?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the tape and the keyboard are made of plastic.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n315887.jpg

Program:

```
 Are A and B made of the same <attr>?
Program:
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='tape')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='keyboard')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the tape made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material is the keyboard made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
